## Session 40 Summary: Fresh Perspective

Attacked the problem from first principles with 6 unconventional experiments. All closed, bringing the total to **531+ approaches tested**.

### Results at a Glance

| Experiment | Idea | Verdict | Failure Mode |
|---|---|---|---|
| Transfer Matrix Sieve | Matrix exponentiation of sieve | FAIL | Equivalence (exp state space) |
| Wavelet Compression | Sparse representation of correction | FAIL | Information (N^{0.75} coefficients) |
| Modular Residue + CRT | Predict p(n) mod q independently | FAIL | Circularity + Information |
| **Carry Propagation Boundary** | Map per-bit difficulty | **NOVEL MEASUREMENT** | Sharp sigmoid, no intermediate bits |
| Ergodic Fast-Forward | Prime gaps as dynamical system | FAIL | Chaotic (positive Lyapunov) |
